29:09.051 --> 29:12.707
23. Never hurt a fly.

29:15.188 --> 29:17.016
Now he done her
to get back at me

29:17.059 --> 29:19.279
for making a joke
at his expense.

29:19.322 --> 29:24.153
His men laughed at him
and he never forgave me.

29:24.197 --> 29:26.982
So he beat her

29:27.026 --> 29:29.680
and strangled her to death.

29:31.291 --> 29:33.293
This man's put a black mark

29:33.336 --> 29:34.816
against the good name
of your regiment.

29:34.860 --> 29:38.167
Now I'm asking you,

29:38.211 --> 29:39.603
as honorable men,

29:39.647 --> 29:40.996
please help me.

29:43.390 --> 29:46.349
Captain John Fitz-Smytth Curzon.
Third Battalion.

29:48.699 --> 29:52.529
I'm asking for your help
as human fucking beings.

29:52.573 --> 29:54.140
