37:10.619 --> 37:12.186
You've spent your
whole life never knowing

37:12.230 --> 37:15.233
if someone's interested in you
or just your name.

37:16.930 --> 37:19.280
Believe me when I say:

37:19.324 --> 37:21.761
it's you he wants.

37:21.804 --> 37:25.243
Your spiritual essence,
not your company.

37:25.286 --> 37:27.854
Wow. You're a good con man.

37:27.897 --> 37:30.726
I can see how you
brainwashed my sister.

37:30.770 --> 37:32.989
You'd need more than
parlor tricks to convince me.

37:33.033 --> 37:35.340
Your brother thinks
I've brainwashed you.

37:35.383 --> 37:38.299
That's ridiculous.

37:38.343 --> 37:40.736
Aleister is just a very
wise and loving man.

37:40.780 --> 37:42.608
A teacher.

37:42.651 --> 37:44.305
Patricia, he's a servant
of the fucking devil.

37:44.349 --> 37:47.047
Martha, I'm trying to make
a deal with this person

37:47.090 --> 37:49.876
and you're making
everything much harder.

37:49.919 --> 37:52.531
Tell me.

37:52.574 --> 37:54.837
How did you two

37:54.881 --> 37:57.449
end up working together?

37:57.492 --> 38:00.060
What was the league thinking?

38:00.103 --> 38:01.844
What league?

38:01.888 --> 38:05.674
Oh, come. I'm not a fool.
The No-Name League.

38:05.718 --> 38:07.894
We're not working
for the No-Name League.

38:07.937 --> 38:09.504
CROWLEY:
Really?

38:09.548 --> 38:12.725
Next, you'll tell me you're
not spying on them for the CIA.

38:12.768 --> 38:16.642
That's a strange idea.

38:16.685 --> 38:18.078
Not true.

38:18.121 --> 38:20.863
You're CIA?
I'm not.

38:22.996 --> 38:24.737
Holy shit.

38:27.000 --> 38:30.569
Of course. I should've guessed.

38:30.612 --> 38:33.485
The CIA? Like...

38:33.528 --> 38:35.008
The CIA?

38:35.051 --> 38:39.665
I am not. Where'd you
get such a notion?

38:39.708 --> 38:42.015
My boss. Where else?THOMAS: Okay, listen,

38:42.058 --> 38:44.322
it is extremely dangerous
to spread that kind of a lie.

38:44.365 --> 38:47.586
Oh. See his teeth?

38:47.629 --> 38:50.893
Yes, deceptively sharp.

38:50.937 --> 38:52.286
There's a beast
inside this one.

38:52.330 --> 38:53.679
PATRICIA:
I am so impressed,

38:53.722 --> 38:56.812
Tommy. For real, the CIA.
Have you killed people?

38:56.856 --> 38:58.597
I repeat, no.

38:58.640 --> 39:02.514
Son of a bitch. CIA? Wow.

39:02.557 --> 39:07.301
Never mind the CIA,
which I'm not a member of.

39:07.345 --> 39:09.172
Let me get
this straight.

39:09.216 --> 39:11.610
In exchange for my sister's
liberty, I have to sell...

39:11.653 --> 39:13.438
I have to sell

39:13.481 --> 39:15.483
my soul to the devil.

39:15.527 --> 39:18.051
Precisely. What do you say?

39:18.094 --> 39:20.270
I'll give you 50,000
to hand her over.

39:20.314 --> 39:22.142
I'm not a goddamn package.

39:22.185 --> 39:23.273
I don't want your money.

39:23.317 --> 39:24.753
If the devil is real,

39:24.797 --> 39:27.277
don't you think my actual soul
is a bit of a high price

39:27.321 --> 39:29.715
to stop you debauching my
sister. She's not Snow White.

39:29.758 --> 39:32.457
200,000 pounds.Fuck you.

39:32.500 --> 39:36.156
You get much more
than Patricia in return.

39:36.199 --> 39:38.724
You get my master's
eternal friendship.

39:38.767 --> 39:41.117
You're a smart
businessman,

39:41.161 --> 39:42.554
Mr. Wayne, think of that.

39:42.597 --> 39:44.817
Think of the power you'll have.

39:44.860 --> 39:46.384
I have power now, you fool.

39:46.427 --> 39:48.255
I can buy and sell
the likes of you.

39:48.298 --> 39:49.996
See now, there's
the beast inside of you.

39:50.039 --> 39:52.694
The real Thomas Wayne
is emerging.

39:52.738 --> 39:55.654
Okay.

39:55.697 --> 39:58.657
Fine. I'll play along

39:58.700 --> 40:01.790
with your ludicrous charade.
You're Lucifer's servant.

40:01.834 --> 40:03.705
I don't negotiate

40:03.749 --> 40:06.578
with underlings.
Let me speak with your boss.

40:06.621 --> 40:09.319
Well, as a rule, he doesn't
grant personal audiences,

40:09.363 --> 40:12.410
except for saints
and the like,

40:12.453 --> 40:14.673
but there's no harm
in asking.
Mm.

40:29.296 --> 40:33.387
So, you want to meet the devil?

40:33.431 --> 40:36.216
No, I don't.

40:36.259 --> 40:39.698
And I'm confident I won't.

40:39.741 --> 40:42.614
But supposing you do?

40:42.657 --> 40:46.313
Suppose you meet him. Will you
listen to what he has to say?

40:46.356 --> 40:48.228
Can we get on with this, please?

40:48.271 --> 40:51.361
I'm curious to see what
hocus pocus you've cooked up.

40:53.233 --> 40:54.669
Good enough.

41:00.240 --> 41:02.895
Ooh.

41:19.389 --> 41:20.478
Okay.

41:27.615 --> 41:29.530
All right.

41:36.537 --> 41:37.843
Hmm.

41:47.026 --> 41:48.244
Really?

41:48.288 --> 41:50.159
Blue movies?

41:58.559 --> 42:00.169
Oh...

42:31.505 --> 42:32.898
JASON:
Fucking lunatic, that one.

42:32.941 --> 42:34.682
Got the devil in her.

42:34.726 --> 42:36.945
So to speak.

42:46.738 --> 42:49.828
Your family must have been
a right old mess

42:49.871 --> 42:51.438
to turn a woman that way.

42:53.658 --> 42:55.529
Did you ever have a go?

42:55.573 --> 42:57.183
If you haven't,

42:57.226 --> 42:59.794
you should.Turn it off.

42:59.838 --> 43:01.579
Turn it off!

43:01.622 --> 43:03.363
I said turn it off!

43:06.496 --> 43:07.933
You missed the best part.

44:18.830 --> 44:21.484
And you say there's
no beast in you.

44:29.188 --> 44:31.451
Christ...

44:35.368 --> 44:38.110
Now, be honest, Thomas.

44:38.153 --> 44:41.679
Tell me you didn't
meet the devil.

44:44.638 --> 44:48.033
PATRICIA:
Christ, Tommy, what...

44:48.076 --> 44:49.687
Let's go.No. Aleister! Help!

44:49.730 --> 44:52.733
Please be at
peace, Patricia.

44:54.343 --> 44:57.869
Your brother and I
understand each other now.

44:57.912 --> 45:01.960
You must do what he
wants. I command it.

45:02.003 --> 45:04.223
Patricia!

45:04.266 --> 45:06.051
No...

45:13.449 --> 45:15.103
Goodbye, all.

45:16.670 --> 45:19.891
Officers stick
together always.

45:19.934 --> 45:21.936
How do you know Curzon
and the Fusiliers

45:21.980 --> 45:23.938
aren't sending some
fucker to do you in?

45:23.982 --> 45:26.419
I don't.Don't you worry, Baz.

45:26.462 --> 45:28.247
Who they gonna send, eh?

45:28.290 --> 45:30.945
I'd like to see
the regular army boys

45:30.989 --> 45:32.860
that are gallus
enough to try us.

45:32.904 --> 45:35.907
The famous last words
of many good men.

45:45.612 --> 45:46.918
You're betting blind, Alfie.

45:46.961 --> 45:48.571
I've got no choice.

45:48.615 --> 45:49.921
This is Curzon's game.

45:49.964 --> 45:51.444
I have to play the cards
in front of me.

45:52.924 --> 45:55.143
SID:
Well, lads, same again?

45:55.187 --> 45:57.015
Aye.Any squaddies been in?

45:57.058 --> 45:58.712
Squaddies? No.
I don't encourage 'em.

46:00.061 --> 46:01.497
Barring present company,

46:01.541 --> 46:03.978
naturally.

46:04.022 --> 46:06.198
Sandra not about?She's upstairs.

46:06.241 --> 46:08.635
She's got the hump with you.
She won't say why.

46:08.678 --> 46:10.376
Oh, that's funny.

46:10.419 --> 46:11.812
SID:
Yeah, funny that.

46:11.856 --> 46:13.596
What's that about, then?

46:13.640 --> 46:15.120
Couldn't tell you.

46:15.163 --> 46:18.384
Funny.

46:18.427 --> 46:21.213
I'll have a word
when I see her.

46:21.256 --> 46:24.216
But listen,
if I don't see her,

46:24.259 --> 46:26.609
tell her I say I'm sorry.About what?

46:26.653 --> 46:27.741
Well, whatever it is.

46:29.874 --> 46:31.353
Right.

46:51.896 --> 46:53.419
Your man will be there
tomorrow night.

46:53.462 --> 46:54.812
Room seven.

46:57.553 --> 47:00.513
ALFRED: This is from
General Malcolm.

47:03.037 --> 47:06.693
DAVEBOY:
See, Mr. Doom and Gloom?

47:06.736 --> 47:09.435
No bother.BAZZA: Or a trap.

47:11.219 --> 47:12.307
We better go in early

47:12.351 --> 47:14.353
and heavy.

47:14.396 --> 47:15.658
No, I don't think so.

47:15.702 --> 47:18.052
I think this is a one-man job.No.

47:18.096 --> 47:20.141
It's not.
Don't be daft.

47:20.185 --> 47:22.883
You're in a dark
frame of mind, Alfred.

47:22.927 --> 47:24.015
You must treat this man

47:24.058 --> 47:25.407
like any other target.

47:25.451 --> 47:27.061
You could be taking on
a whole regiment.

47:27.105 --> 47:29.281
Well, then, one or two more men
won't make any odds, will they?

47:29.324 --> 47:31.413
No, I know this place.

47:31.457 --> 47:33.024
It's a one-man job. Cheers.

47:33.067 --> 47:37.637
♪ Don't you change
the things you do ♪

47:37.680 --> 47:40.945
♪ Only time can tell
if we get on well... ♪

47:40.988 --> 47:42.947
"Mars is in the house
of Aquarius,

47:42.990 --> 47:47.168
"so this will be a good time
for you to take decisive action

47:47.212 --> 47:50.345
in your business
and personal life."

47:50.389 --> 47:53.087
Stop wriggling.

47:53.131 --> 47:57.526
"But beware false friends
and empty promises."

48:00.921 --> 48:01.879
Hmm.

48:01.922 --> 48:03.489
Hmm?

48:03.532 --> 48:06.796
Well, you know who
that's about, don't you?

48:06.840 --> 48:08.320
Your lady doctor.

48:09.887 --> 48:11.105
You can laugh now,

48:11.149 --> 48:13.368
but what if she's
told on us?

48:13.412 --> 48:15.849
What if the police are
closing in on us as we speak?

48:15.893 --> 48:17.720
You needn't worry, Peg.

48:17.764 --> 48:19.331
Frances has no
falsity in her.

48:19.374 --> 48:21.028
She's not capable
of treachery

48:21.072 --> 48:23.291
or cowardice, poor soul.

48:25.380 --> 48:27.948
Oh, I like that color.

48:27.992 --> 48:29.558
Do me next, eh?

48:29.602 --> 48:32.083
As it happens, my dear,
I think I can offer you

48:32.126 --> 48:35.477
a much better service
than that.

48:35.521 --> 48:38.350
I've been talking quietly to
some old Raven Society friends.

48:38.393 --> 48:40.352
Well-connected types.

48:40.395 --> 48:43.007
And there's news of your old
friend, Alfred Pennyworth.

48:43.050 --> 48:45.139
Oh?

48:45.183 --> 48:46.619
Resourceful young man.

48:46.662 --> 48:48.577
It seems he's found out
who killed his fiancée.

48:51.754 --> 48:52.842
Esme.

48:52.886 --> 48:55.193
I thought you'd like to know.

48:55.236 --> 48:58.848
Who did it?
Where are they?

49:06.639 --> 49:09.294
MARTHA:
Thomas.

49:09.337 --> 49:10.948
Huh?

49:10.991 --> 49:13.602
Will you please tell us
what happened?

49:20.479 --> 49:22.960
Nothing happened.

49:23.003 --> 49:24.787
You saw him, didn't you?

49:29.488 --> 49:31.446
We were never there.

49:33.448 --> 49:35.842
Not any of us.

49:35.885 --> 49:37.278
You understand?

49:50.813 --> 49:51.945
You saw him.

49:59.039 --> 50:00.823
No.

51:11.068 --> 51:12.199
You?!

51:12.243 --> 51:15.072
Shh! Quiet.

51:15.115 --> 51:17.857
ALFRED:
Hey, you're supposed to be dead.

51:17.900 --> 51:19.293
SYKES:
Well, I'm not, am I?

51:19.337 --> 51:20.425
Let's get on with it.

51:31.566 --> 51:33.481
How do you know
it's him?

51:33.525 --> 51:35.440
Let me handle this.

51:50.759 --> 51:51.847
Come on.

52:05.034 --> 52:06.819
Get the bastard!

53:29.162 --> 53:30.772
You're supposed to be dead.

53:30.816 --> 53:33.297
Well, I'm not, am I?

53:33.340 --> 53:36.996
That was your bloody doing.

53:37.039 --> 53:38.258
I had the bastard.

53:41.522 --> 53:45.570
GAUNT:
Our enemies call us zealots.

53:45.613 --> 53:48.181
And they are correct.

53:48.225 --> 53:51.402
Zealots we are, and proud of it.

53:53.882 --> 53:57.712
When did rigor and discipline

53:57.756 --> 54:02.195
and duty become terms of abuse?

54:02.239 --> 54:06.417
And who were the great
men and women of history

54:06.460 --> 54:08.636
who changed the world?

54:08.680 --> 54:11.422
Moderates? No!

54:11.465 --> 54:14.207
Zealots, like you and I!

54:14.251 --> 54:15.208
People of faith.

54:17.341 --> 54:18.994
MAN: That's right!MAN 2: Well said.

54:19.038 --> 54:23.216
Those citizens that are not

54:23.260 --> 54:25.174
loyal patriots

54:25.218 --> 54:27.960
shall be silenced.

54:28.003 --> 54:31.877
Those foreigners
who are not our friends

54:31.920 --> 54:33.618
shall be expelled.

54:35.794 --> 54:40.146
We shall put down
sexual deviants,

54:40.189 --> 54:41.974
and we shall hang thieves!

54:44.933 --> 54:46.413
Yes!

54:48.502 --> 54:51.679
The Raven Society,
ladies and gentlemen,

54:51.723 --> 54:55.770
is on the cusp of a new dawn.

54:55.814 --> 55:00.645
We shall lurk in the shadows
no longer.

55:00.688 --> 55:06.346
A revelation is coming
that will shock the world.

55:06.390 --> 55:08.130
I promise you,

55:08.174 --> 55:10.350
it'll shock the world!

55:10.394 --> 55:12.265
Are you with me?!

55:13.484 --> 55:15.573
Are you with me?! Yes!

